teacher_info.about_teacher:
I provide informal tutoring as well as teach structured lessons. All my classes are personalized to each of my students and in order to figure out what you need exactly we will discuss all your goals for our upcoming sessions in our first introductory lesson. 
I provide my students with:
♦ learning materials whether they are books, texts for reading, listening tasks or video links;
♦ pdf files/exercises/presentations/listening tasks I make myself to ensure that you're working on your weaknesses;
♦ feedback

teacher_info.teaching_style:
What the lessons include:

- learning new words and expressions on the chosen topic depending on the student's level;

- listening and analysis of audio materials (learning to perceive information by ear);

- reading (learning to perceive information visually, working on pronunciation);

- conversational practice (we analyze real situations from business or everyday life, depending on the student's level).

After the lesson, I send a link to a file with the vocabulary, grammar, exercises for practicing.

If you want to pay more attention to a particular category (conversational practice/writing/reading), we will do it without compromising the result!
